<h4>Listing with forms</h4>
<p>In Listing with forms, make sure that the <code>id</code> of the <code>select</code> element is the same as the <code>data-target</code> of the list <code>ol</code>.</p>
<p>Example:</p>
<pre class="yondu__code"><code>&lt;select multiple <b>id=&quot;select2&quot;</b> data-title=&quot;Endorser&quot; class=&quot;form-control abcom-list__dropdown abcom-form&quot; &gt;</code></pre>
<pre class="yondu__code"><code>&lt;ol class=&quot;abcom-list&quot; <b>data-parent=&quot;select2&quot;</b>&gt;</code></pre>

